title: Newly Renovated 3 Bed/3 Bath Apartment Homes-Open Weekends For Tours!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
